"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"不過總部就未必再落腳腥港"},{"pid":"8d0d845abce2205d24c29df6c08742978197b822","tid":2375592,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"你見到熱錢繼續流入，資金繼續自由進出<br />\n<br />\n成個賭局繼續開門做生意<br />\n<br />\n只要一日班鬼佬喺香港賺到嘅錢可以繼續有信心拎得走<br />\n<br />\n佢哋自然唔會走資 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本攬炒就郁唔到佢成個融資機制<br />\n<br />\n攬炒2019年做唔到嘅嘢2020年武肺做到晒<br />\n<br />\n但係都影響唔到佢成個融資機制，只係影響到低下階層各行各業。<br />\n<br />\n隨着登登上台，佢嘅經濟實力隨時起幾年之內攀升到亞洲第一大，到是香港嗰舊錢對佢來講只係雞毛蒜皮。  要制衡到佢難道就會更高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f36bb7b84fdb179afe99ac751feb7d886ef2f2","tid":2375592,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"仲理咩鬼香港<br />\n移民攬炒最實際"},{"pid":"4b0f5e3e00c7530e75a84cbc6f20c3213a427093","tid":2375592,"uid":258903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"仲要奶?"},{"pid":"057e60b1695b62e797e87abd2756de2a264655c4","tid":2375592,"uid":60563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"353fb78b6e046f2f1fc1540e705818c700946236","tid":2375592,"uid":122377,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"下 連登仔又話外資走哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"連登不嬲同現實係兩個時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08236c3d7f64f7d8a6e70e0696f0a9ee5635040","tid":2375592,"uid":45925,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:18:37.000Z","msg":"鬼佬喺 remote office 做 transaction 做 deal , 香港市面變成地獄都 冇撚所為，<br />\n總之交易個 server 開住機就有人民幣轉美元收錢"},{"pid":"418eba11fac2c4744f16f187f042227c0a52616a","tid":2375592,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike"